description:
Welcome to Open Tabs! The show where I leave all of the tabs open on my browser and go through them with you! 

Today, I sit down with my cousin Andrew and my producer Halston. We go through Jackson Mahomes Kansas Apartment, Pam & Tommy, Andrew’s college girlfriend leaving him for Sebastian Stan, disk golf, ice climbers, German tourists, Oliver Tree, Please don’t destroy, and much more! 

 

For all TOUR DATE & MERCH click HERE: http://www.bertbertbert.com
